---
// Jika nanti kamu ingin menggunakan foto asli, kamu tinggal ganti inisial dengan tag img

---

<section id="testimonials" class="px-5 md:px-10 py-24 bg-[#090c09] relative overflow-hidden">
   

    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-neon font-barlow-cond text-[0.75rem] font-bold tracking-[0.35em] uppercase mb-4">
        <span class="w-[30px] h-[1px] bg-neon"></span> Social Proof
      </div>
      <h2 class="font-bebas text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,6rem)] leading-[0.95] text-white section-reveal">
        APA KATA<br><span class="neon-text">MEREKA</span>
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-5 mt-16 section-reveal">
        
        <div class="bg-card border border-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:border-neon/20 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-yellow-500 shadow-yellow-500/20">
                <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z" />
              </svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Lapangan sintetisnya mantap banget! Ga bikin lutut sakit, dan cahayanya pas buat malem. Tim gw udah langganan tiap minggu."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-neon to-neon-dim flex items-center justify-center font-bebas text-dark text-xl shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(57,255,20,0.2)]">
              R
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-barlow-cond font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Rizky Pratama</div>
              <div class="text-white/35 text-[0.8rem]">Kapten Tim FC Karawang</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:border-neon/20 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-yellow-500">
                <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z" />
              </svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Gym-nya lengkap parah. Peralatan baru semua, AC dingin, dan instrukturnya helpful. Worth it buat member bulanan!"
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-neon to-neon-dim flex items-center justify-center font-bebas text-dark text-xl shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(57,255,20,0.2)]">
              D
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-barlow-cond font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Diana Kusuma</div>
              <div class="text-white/35 text-[0.8rem]">Fitness Enthusiast</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-card border border-white/5 p-8 transition-all hover:border-neon/20 hover:-translate-y-1 group">
          <div class="flex gap-1 mb-4">
            {[1, 2, 3, 4, 5].map(() => (
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="text-yellow-500">
                <path d="M12 17.27L18.18 21l-1.64-7.03L22 9.24l-7.19-.61L12 2 9.19 8.63 2 9.24l5.46 4.73L5.82 21z" />
              </svg>
            ))}
          </div>
          <p class="text-white/70 text-[0.95rem] leading-relaxed mb-6 italic">
            "Booking gampang banget! WhatsApp langsung dibalas, bayar transfer, beres. Cafenya juga enak buat nongkrong abis main."
          </p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-neon to-neon-dim flex items-center justify-center font-bebas text-dark text-xl shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(57,255,20,0.2)]">
              A
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="font-barlow-cond font-bold text-white uppercase tracking-wide">Agung Santoso</div>
              <div class="text-white/35 text-[0.8rem]">Regular Player</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
</section>